<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>public<sp/>API<sp/>추가<sp/>금지</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>`text-atlas-renderer.*`<sp/>수정은<sp/>아직<sp/>금지</highlight></codeline>
